	The Taxicode / Taxi Price Compare app is an app developed by Web3r.
	It uses the Taxicode API to allow users to make and take bookings
	online via the phones.

	The app is developed using PhoneGap and is written in HTML, CSS and
	Javascript. It is designed to be deployed to iOS and Android devices
	and potentially Kindle/Blackberries/Windows 8 Phones in the long run.

	Following is a list of remaining requirements.

##########################################################################################################

	REMAINING REQUIREMENTS
	
	Auto Update Stuff

	1.	Google Maps - Auto-reload at startup until loaded.
	2.	Bookings - Auto-update when loaded.
	3.	Bookings - Load bookings of logged in user.

	Booking Engine

	1.	Error handling.
	2.	Send off user when booking if logged in.
	3.	Option to save storage option if logged in.
	4.	Booking with saved card.
	5.	Send mode so that it just returns Taxicode partners for Taxicode and all for Taxi Price Compare.

	Directory

	1.	All of it...

	Users

	1.	User token to authenticate instead of cookies. Token keeps user signed in.
	2.	Create User

	Glitches

	1.	Input Date/Month/Time replacement.
	2.	Menu bars disappearing.

	Last Touches

	1.	Get SSL Certificate for api server.
	2.	Update domains.
	3.	Remove console stuff.

##########################################################################################################

	EXTRA REQUIREMENTS

	Booking Engine

	1.	Rebook journey.
	2.	Select from recent locations.

	Users

	1.	Fully implement user management.
		- Change Password
		- Forgot Password
		- Edit Details
		- Authenticate user with text/in app.

